{"type": "article", "id": 60487, "title": "这款水磨石风格的无线充电器，拿来做装饰品也不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-21T22:47:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 19254, "name": "Away"}, {"id": 56113, "name": "ames"}, {"id": 56114, "name": "Vanessa Barragão"}, {"id": 56115, "name": "B 印 YOSHIDA"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190121210545Gj6L0vy9mH3VMTWu.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Native Union Dock Wireless Charger Terrazzo Edition</h3><p>水磨石近几年成为大热材料，设计师和建筑师们都对它有所偏爱。最近，科技配件品牌 Native Union 也加入到了这股潮流中，推出了水磨石版本的 Dock 无线充电器。</p><p>标志性的色彩斑点和随机图案是水磨石材料的最突出特点。但 Native Union 用的不是传统的水泥基底水磨石，而是使用复合材料 Jermonite，这是一种更轻的替代品，但仍能够再现水磨石风格。</p><p>这个水磨石版本的 Dock 无线充电器，适用于任何 Qi 兼容设备，包括 iPhone 8，iPhone 8 Plus，iPhone X，iPhone Xs，iPhone Xs Max，iPhone XR，Galaxy S9 / Samsung Galaxy Note9 和 Google Pixel 3 / 3XL 等。由于制造工艺的性质，每个充电器都是手工制作，具有独一无二的图案，售价 149.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.nativeunion.com/dock-wireless-charger-terrazzo-edition/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121210659GM9xSO38Ed2W4qUi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658594\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121210659ColrBEzUDpGV7AiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121210700qCPHMhYFLJi2ubGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121210701XflLBvuxZszDVhSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121210700GhyZQRrEOINpPUHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901212107011DhFdaBCHcqfJmLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>B 印 ヨシダ × 博多織 / 2WAY HELMET BAG</h3><p>由日本时尚百货 BEAMS 与 Yoshida 合作创立的品牌 B 印 YOSHIDA，最近找来拥有 777 年历史的日本传统工艺“博多织”合作推出特别版包袋系列。</p><p>整个系列以最为经典的 Helmet Bag 为基础，分别推出灰白及深蓝两种配色，整体以帆布物料作主轴，并为袋前两个口袋换上了由“博多织”所织造的图案布料，售价 30240 日元，<a href=\"https://www.beams.co.jp/item/bjirushi/bag/34612053176/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204001BXpKWmJFvVer3C0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121203913aWQRElJhquU3064d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121203914UTxuiQ37NShYqpFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121203914He4aOySKcwD6shGL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>OCEAN  TAPESTRY<b> </b>by Vanessa Barragão</h3><p>葡萄牙设计工作室 Vanessa Barragão 利用回收的废纱来制作纺织产品。纤维的处理、染色等化工过程、机器能耗和织物废料，使纺织工业成为了世界上污染最严重的行业之一。Vanessa Barragão 认识到了其中的危害，特别是在海洋上，海洋吸收了地球大气中 90%的多余热量。海平面以下几米的空间储存的热量与地球整个大气层的热量一样多。如果海洋升温太快，珊瑚和藻类等物种就会受到威胁。</p><p>Vanessa Barragão 利用废弃的工业纤维制作海洋挂毯，向地球的生命之源致敬。这种对回收利用的执着表明了艺术家对工业生产方式的不妥协。所有材料都是从当地工厂的存货中回收的，清洗后用来制作手工织物。设计师利用诸如挂钩、制毯法、织平针、流苏花边和钩针编织之类的古老技术来制作挂毯中的海洋图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204035NnV6hDpJZbwo0U9r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204035bCnFfY70TKjOckQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204035tYZa6i8TCOgxKsof.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901212040366J3nbrx1ltVW2ECY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204036wKItl97dUERo2fNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204036bP1aCp0OD2Kno9M7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171149\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.vanessabarragao.com/ocean-tapestry\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vanessa Barragão</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Maraca Lounge Chair by Sebastian Herkner for ames</h3><p>去年，德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 与设计品牌 ames 合作推出了 CARIBE 系列。今年，双方再度合作推出了一款名为 Maraca 的户外休闲椅，其特色是充满趣味的色彩组合，灵感来源于传统的哥伦比亚吊床。</p><p>轻松的金属结构搭配编织羊毛座椅，Maraca 目前提供三种配色：verde /púrpura/ rojo - menta，naranja / dorado / rojo - carne，dorado /púrpura/ rojo - black。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204135lb0okaWTeLgG2tEr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.807813\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204135UvQqMjngVmfAeWtX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204137GiILmpsw4F0BPhU7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204138GaeS9UoE7KcfYn64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204138RFEsxeUcIqBCZwGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204139tAq2yO8iHlzRCFPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.ames-shop.de/en/lines/maraca/ames-maraca-lounge-chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">ames</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Latest Limited Edition Collection - On View by Away</h3><p>创立于 2015 年的旅行箱品牌 Away，致力于将一个行李箱的设计和科技以及高雅的设计结合在一起，以此创造一个生活方式品牌，也许还会做成一个以旅行爱好者为基础的社区。</p><p>最近，它们推出限量版 On View 系列，意在使旅行更加有趣和方便，鼓励用户更加自由地表达自我。这款改良的聚碳酸酯材质手提箱，外部采用条纹纹理样式的彩色色调，目前有两种颜色可供选择，包括 Pastel 款（粉红色外壳和暖色调条纹），以及 Ink 款（深蓝色和蓝色系条纹）。Pastel 和 Ink 款有四种尺寸可供选择：Carry-On，Bigger Carry-on，Medium 和 The Large。售价 275 美元，<a href=\"https://www.awaytravel.com/on-view/carry-on\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204253JnMEIUDcNvOre4fq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204229IOg0L6yAKnqr39e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.961719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204229bd3S4zopT7xwBYAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.811719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204230h4GdPW98AvRkzfeS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190121204230UiApQdDTv12VgjyH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.856250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}